1. Register with SendGrid for the free plan
2. Verify account when you receive the email
3. Click your username and in top left and then setup guide
4. Click Start next to "Integrate using our Web API or SMTP relay"
5. Click the Choose button below SMTP relay
6. Enter a name for your application, and click Create Key
7. Your SMTP details will be populated below with your new API key as the password


We’ll need those details for the following test (we do this bit)
8. Enter these details into your Skyve application
9. Restart the Skyve application
10. Test an email by inviting a new user
 
You then do this
11. Return to SendGrid, check I've updated my settings and click Verify Integration


